  SKYES OVER LONDON — ULTIMATE ENVIRONMENT VARIABLE TEMPLATE
  The single source of truth for every secret, token, and config var
  across the entire Sky0s platform ecosystem.
================================================================================

HOW THIS WORKS
──────────────
Every platform in this project funnels auth through ONE lane:
  - AI calls      → 0megaSkyeGate (Cloudflare Worker)
  - Identity      → SuperIDE Worker (Cloudflare Worker + Neon DB)
  - Errors        → kAIxU-Brain / SkyErrors (Cloudflare Worker + D1 + KV + R2)
  - Mail          → SkyeMail 2.0 (Netlify Functions + Neon DB)
  - Commerce      → SkyeHubs (Netlify Functions + Stripe + Neon DB)

The master shared secrets are:
  KAIXU_ADMIN_TOKEN       → proves you are the sovereign admin owner
  KAIXU_APP_TOKEN         → proves a platform is a trusted app caller
  RUNNER_SHARED_SECRET    → proves the SuperIDE worker call is internal
  KAIXU_SERVICE_SECRET    → proves kAIxU-Brain can talk to SuperIDE gate
  OMEGA_GATE_URL          → the one URL every platform points AI calls at

UPDATE SEQUENCE WHEN ROTATING SECRETS
──────────────────────────────────────
1. Generate new secret value
2. Update wrangler secret:  npx wrangler secret put <NAME> --name <worker>
3. Update Netlify UI:        Site Settings → Environment Variables
4. Update .dev.vars locally for each worker
5. Restart workers / redeploy functions
6. Verify /health endpoints return 200 on all platforms

